21 void analogReadCallback(const pumpkin_messages::analog_arrayConstPtr& msg) {
22  for (int i = 0; i < MAX_N_A_READS; i++) {
23  if (msg->an_read[i] > max_a_reads[i])
24  max_a_reads[i] = msg->an_read[i];

27  angles[i] = map((uint16_t)msg->an_read[i], min_a_reads[i], max_a_reads[i], 0.0, 180.0);
28  }
29  ROS_INFO("Angle: [%f]", angles[0]);
30 }
